what is bridgelabz?

BridgeLabz is an AWS recognised incubator and is solely focussed on solving tech employability. Over the last 4 years, it has worked with 300+ top tech companies and 1500+ engineers have been hired from Bridgelabz. It has labs in Mumbai and Bangalore. It has partnered with over 300 companies, including Yatra, Capgemini, Meru Cabs, LafargeHolcim, JDA, UrbanLadder, Fullerton India and RBL bank.
